.SS "buffer\.readUInt8(offset, bigEndian)"
Reads an unsigned 8 bit integer from the buffer at the specified offset\. If \fBbigEndian\fR is true, reads bytes in a big endian format, otherwise reads them as
little endian\.
.
.P
Example:
.
.IP "" 4
.
.nf
